COMMODORE (R) ANNOUNCES AMIGA 3000 (R) WITH SCALA (R)
PACKAGE AT OUTSTANDING NEW PRICE OF $1499*

(West Chester, PA --- September 24, 1992) --- Commodore Business
Machines, Inc. today announced that its Amiga (R) 3000 Presentation
System, bundled with the new SCALA (R)  Multimedia 200 software, is
now available in the U.S. through the end of November* at the
outstanding promotional price of $1499. Prior to this promotion, the
package had a suggested retail price of over $3100*. Now, promotion
savings range from $1725 to $2015*, depending on the system purchased.

The Amiga 3000 Presentation System along with the SCALA Multimedia
200 software provides a dynamic, easy-to-use, professional package that
enables users to create spectacular graphic presentations. The two
presentation system offerings are: the A3000-25/50 system at the
promotional price of $1499*; and the A3000-25/100 system at the
promotional price of $1859*. Both systems offer the full capabilities of
the Amiga 3000. 

"The Amiga 3000 Presentation System is designed to meet the growing
need for dynamic presentations within the corporate, government,
education and small to medium-size business marketplaces. Business
presentations represent one of the largest growth segments for
computer-based multimedia systems. Commodore's price offering, with its
outstanding savings, provides a special incentive and opportunity for
presentation professionals," commented Geoff Stilley, Commodore Vice
President of Professional Sales. 

To find an authorized Commodore dealer near you call (800) 66-AMIGA.

Commodore Business Machines, Inc., based in West Chester, PA, is the
U.S. subsidiary of Commodore International Limited. The company
manufactures and markets a complete line of Amiga computers and
peripherals for the business, consumer, education and government markets.

Commodore (R) is a trademark of Commodore Electronics Limited. Amiga
(R) is a trademark of Commodore-Amiga, Inc. SCALA (R) is a trademark
of Scala Inc.

*Savings and retail prices are based on Manufacturer's Suggested Retail
Prices. Promotional pricing is not valid in conjunction with any other
offer or promotion. Available while quantities last at participating
authorized resellers through November 30, 1992.

